creator: Kwalee Ltd
descriptionHtml:
On your marks, get set, SPRAY!

It’s time to let the crazy adventures begin, with Foam Climber! Armed with your trusty foam gun, race against your fellow competitors, dodging obstacles and creating paths! Point and spray your foam to create a bubble mountain to climb, or use the foam gun as a bridge over the dreaded spike pits!
Be careful, fall between the gaps and it’s the lava pit for you!

Do you have what it takes to become number one?

Foam Climber features:
- Create your own paths
- Race against others
- Heart racing gameplay
- Multiple worlds to discover
- A variety of challenging puzzles to face

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: + Bug fixes and improvements to keep you spraying foam!
